{"id": "1186986390987223112", "channel_id": "1186986390987223112", "type": 0, "author_id": "1181025751710056449", "author_name": "0sgtq0", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一次防御有效果添加胚胎进度，之后的防御好像在固定序号的防御中失去添加胚胎进度的效果\n\n明明中毒都触发了，却不加胚胎进度。\n\n在深潜中初次战斗，单独实验了4次，均发现未触发添加胚胎进度效果。\n\n以前玩就感觉哪里不对劲，因为防御卡打的快没有特意去记，今天特意去复现了这个bug\n\n希望能快点修复，这个命轮还挺好用的。☹️", "timestamp": "2023-12-20T11:00:08.752000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1186986391696048168", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-41-43-221_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 168945, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186986390987223112/1186986391696048168/Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-41-43-221_com.miui.video.jpg?ex=6a006538&is=69ff13b8&hm=e6c6105f866bebe4d947905120eb74ad2fefc9acc1fdb270088d6e3e16f5d01e&"}, {"id": "1186986392761409536", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-29-126_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 172864, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186986390987223112/1186986392761409536/Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-29-126_com.miui.video.jpg?ex=6a006539&is=69ff13b9&hm=af72d379a7b6e433e1fb4c010e03837177c3fc71c191583b099501f65cbd6453&"}, {"id": "1186986393562525767", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-33-211_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 169462, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186986390987223112/1186986393562525767/Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-33-211_com.miui.video.jpg?ex=6a006539&is=69ff13b9&hm=bc390849a15fe5b02b07c01d7be436505def9131e570690013f1752ef04c21d6&"}, {"id": "1186986393889669140", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-38-407_com.miui.video.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 170861, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186986390987223112/1186986393889669140/Screenshot_2023-12-20-18-42-38-407_com.miui.video.jpg?ex=6a006539&is=69ff13b9&hm=ce80fc3b7a451c29f7b24777fe59e17bab899b87d696a4926096f7232889a31c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1186986390987223112", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」阿格里帕命轮效果未触发添加胚胎进度", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1186943382556246057", "channel_id": "1186943382556246057", "type": 0, "author_id": "559372472177131520", "author_name": "nightglass0424", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前麥卡儲值活動用點數換到的東西\n但完全不知道怎麼使用", "timestamp": "2023-12-20T08:09:14.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1186943383235735622", "filename": "Screenshot_2023-12-20-16-06-38-75_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131040, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1186943382556246057/1186943383235735622/Screenshot_2023-12-20-16-06-38-75_6120889c12ac7e9ba4b3ef1f073858ff.jpg?ex=6a003d2a&is=69feebaa&hm=857a7006d308aea6379c81fb147fa4023f78bb14ebc9e37d2a53c2ecb1bdb901&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1186943382556246057", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」請問「秘銀交易憑證」是什麼", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1186953794924331008", "channel_id": "1186953794924331008", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185926972984020993", "author_name": "yonaka177", "author_bot": false, "content": "PVP方面（僅代表個人體驗而言）：\n請問官方是否有考慮過將寧菲亞進行削弱呢？本來pvp的血量就不多，在寧菲亞疊了60+毒以後更是幾乎沒有翻盤的餘地，哪怕朵兒進行了淨化，其餘角色的毒也是十分致命的打擊。而現在pvp大多數走的都是後期爆發流，而黏著性如此強且能瞬發的群攻是否有些破壞平衡了呢？希望官方可以關注看看。\n以及希萊斯特是否有考慮將延遲奶改成瞬發奶並且削弱奶量？對比起朵兒能復活又能瞬發奶，希萊斯特在奶媽方面似乎後勁不足，就連淨化也是延遲⋯⋯\n\n命輪方面：\n考慮到大家在抽命輪時肯定不僅僅有考慮pve的需求，也會有pvp的需求，在命輪介紹那裡是否能放上pvp方面的介紹呢？以及在pvp裡可不可以也看見未擁有的命輪技能效果好讓玩家能在配隊時綜合更多思路去搭配隊伍呢？\n\n以上僅是我個人意見，可能有不成熟的地方先說聲抱歉，十分感謝閱讀🥺🥺🥺", "timestamp": "2023-12-20T08:50:37.245000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1186953794924331008", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」關於PVP和命輪介紹的意見", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
